summary: This is a lovely little camp near hunters rest, there is a map marker showing the loacation of the camp.
descriptionHtml:
This is a lovely little camp near hunters rest. I have not yet added everything there is still a little bit of work left to do but all of that shell be done in time. This camp is also companion friendly.

Locations is by the hunters rest, just look at the images. And there is also a map marker leading to the location.

I am open to suggestions though if you have anything you would like me to add or if you have found anything wrong with the camp please message me or write on the comments page and tell me what is happening =)

And also if you want to change something yourself i have no problem with it. I dont mind if you guys go throwing it around the internet on different websites and so on. 

And if you want to use this in your mod you dont need to ask im not fussy. I suppose it would be nice if you gave me some credit but im not going to get all angry over it. Just use this how you all want to use it a hunting camp, a resource, a break away from the big city, a bandit camp, the foundation of a mod you are creating. 

The future of this mod all comes down to you =)
author: cdsparey

files.changelogHtml:
Fixed: Chest said Angrs chest because and the reason why was because i ticked \'show owner\' in the options menu which would show it as me which is bad so now it should just say hide chest.
fixed: If you dont know all ready just down the road is a big talos shrine i put it behind some tress so its abit harder to see for you all you thalmor fans =)
fixed: The wagon wheel was suppose to be up against the work bench which it was not so i changed that.
fixed: The bed had some very minor clipping issues only noticeable if you really looked so i changed that so it fits nice and snug.
Change: I change the logs holding the door to something different seeing as the originals were snowy which did not making any sense seeing as there is no snow in that particular area
